|---------------------------- |----- |-------- |----------------- |--------:|---------:|---------:|------:|
|    IteratorLessThanConstant |  Clr |     Clr | Constant operand | 1.285 s | 0.0063 s | 0.0059 s |  1.00 |
| ConstantGreaterThanIterator |  Clr |     Clr | Constant operand | 1.282 s | 0.0021 s | 0.0020 s |  1.00 |
