Based on the above results...

 - If you&#39;re asking if one operator is faster than the other, then I would say no.
 - If you&#39;re asking which operator you should use, I would suggest whichever one you feel gives the greatest readability and clarity to your code since that is much more important than any microoptimization, if one even exists.

